data_table.description: Digital ECG, Original Cohort Exam 11, Offspring Cohort Exam 1, Generation 3 Cohort Exam 1. Cycle is defined as the time from heart beat to the next. Different cardiac cycles were used to obtain different measurements of the same intervals for some variables.

variable.name: shareid
variable.description: UNIQUE PARTICIPANT ID

variable.name: idtype
variable.description: COHORT IDENTIFIER
